<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="86880000t" end="132360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">少在朋友前面耍帅了</p>
<p begin="132610000t" end="148370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">菜月昴</p>
<p begin="155020000t" end="177180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你现在一定因为不知道该怎么做</p>
<p begin="177420000t" end="201500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">脑中混乱不已对吧</p>
<p begin="207750000t" end="232530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">明明一堆事情必须得做</p>
<p begin="232770000t" end="260290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">却因为自己不管是技巧<br />头脑或力量都不足</p>
<p begin="260530000t" end="284450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">让时间就这样白白流逝</p>
<p begin="284700000t" end="300270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">而感到焦虑不已对吧</p>
<p begin="319030000t" end="334090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">听得到吗</p>
<p begin="339790000t" end="364340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">听得到的话就给我点回应啊</p>
<p begin="372250000t" end="389430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">你要做什么</p>
<p begin="405830000t" end="430950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">原以为你只是一时热血被冲昏头而已</p>
<p begin="431190000t" end="449460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">没想到这次竟然连行动都这么草率</p>
<p begin="452980000t" end="482260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">该说真不愧是昴先生的作风吗</p>
<p begin="484910000t" end="494770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">真是丢脸</p>
<p begin="495010000t" end="511200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">是吗</p>
<p begin="568980000t" end="595180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">昴先生的力量不过就如此而已</p>
<p begin="605410000t" end="636290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">在喜欢上的女人面前耍帅就算了</p>
<p begin="643550000t" end="672900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">在对自己有好感的女孩面前耍帅</p>
<p begin="673140000t" end="689090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">也可以原谅</p>
<p begin="693470000t" end="717570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">但是就仅限于此</p>
<p begin="725620000t" end="744120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">你也明白这样是不够的吧</p>
<p begin="747790000t" end="765700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">知道这样是传达不到的吧</p>
<p begin="770140000t" end="794460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">想在喜欢的女孩面前耍帅吧</p>
<p begin="794710000t" end="827500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">想让喜欢自己的女孩感到骄傲对吧</p>
<p begin="837190000t" end="846290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">那么</p>
<p begin="846530000t" end="870460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">稍微借助一下别人的力量又如何</p>
<p begin="876470000t" end="885920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">像是…</p>
<p begin="894420000t" end="905380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">朋友之类的</p>
<p begin="951630000t" end="975810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">我有想过拜托人</p>
<p begin="980260000t" end="996620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">也尝试求助过</p>
<p begin="1005920000t" end="1020630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">但果然还是不行</p>
<p begin="1037960000t" end="1046110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">但是</p>
<p begin="1053470000t" end="1070860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">我并不记得</p>
<p begin="1075930000t" end="1096880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">自己有被昴先生拜托过啊</p>
<p begin="1100480000t" end="1121070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不…不是的</p>
<p begin="1183650000t" end="1203480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">脑袋里乱七八糟的</p>
<p begin="1211600000t" end="1239960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">有一大堆就算说了<br />你也不可能会相信的事</p>
<p begin="1246360000t" end="1268400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">也不知道从何说起…</p>
<p begin="1276370000t" end="1291450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">说说看吧</p>
<p begin="1291690000t" end="1306870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我会听到最后的</p>
<p begin="1313280000t" end="1332460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">不, 可是那样的话…</p>
<p begin="1332700000t" end="1362330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">所以就说少在那边耍帅了</p>
<p begin="1362570000t" end="1390960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">有时间在那边想些鸡毛蒜皮的小事</p>
<p begin="1391200000t" end="1409290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">不如快点全部一五一十地讲出来</p>
<p begin="1409530000t" end="1420230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">就算你这么说</p>
<p begin="1420480000t" end="1425990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">我还是…</p>
<p begin="1426230000t" end="1443270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">快给我把那些杂七杂八的事都讲出来</p>
<p begin="1443510000t" end="1457580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">然后最后只要说</p>
<p begin="1457820000t" end="1480530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">"相信我"就好了</p>
<p begin="1480770000t" end="1496890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">因为我们是朋友啊</p>
<p begin="1560700000t" end="1595480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">虽然你可能不会相信…</p>
<p begin="1725000000t" end="1736460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="1783250000t" end="1796350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">来打个赌吧</p>
<p begin="1796590000t" end="1826000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">将我和你的愿望当作筹码</p>
<p begin="1868480000t" end="1891790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">没想到这一轮的我</p>
<p begin="1892030000t" end="1908330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">竟然有机会</p>
<p begin="1908570000t" end="1936680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">能再和你见到面呢</p>
<p begin="1942780000t" end="1970330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">这次就是我和你最后的对决了</p>
<p begin="1975260000t" end="2002180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">这一轮我一定会拯救圣域</p>
<p begin="2002430000t" end="2020870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">还有宅邸给你看</p>
<p begin="2024690000t" end="2053930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">还要把你所期望的那些给彻底毁掉</p>
<p begin="2057720000t" end="2093820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">你要在这个接近死局的状况中重整态势</p>
<p begin="2098400000t" end="2117900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">要将你唯一的权能</p>
<p begin="2118140000t" end="2135540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">那份力量给放弃吗</p>
<p begin="2148820000t" end="2183760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">能够重来并不代表能够拯救</p>
<p begin="2193520000t" end="2214470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我和你应该都很清楚才对</p>
<p begin="2222670000t" end="2235220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我的这份力量</p>
<p begin="2235460000t" end="2253850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">并不是那么便利的东西啊</p>
<p begin="2267290000t" end="2285330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">就当这次是最后一次好了</p>
<p begin="2290410000t" end="2313380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">那你希望从我这里得到什么</p>
<p begin="2317060000t" end="2336900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我的要求很简单</p>
<p begin="2340410000t" end="2358840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">如果我能将圣域和宅邸</p>
<p begin="2359080000t" end="2375690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">两边都救出来的话</p>
<p begin="2381860000t" end="2405670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">你就必须舍弃那本书和我一起来</p>
<p begin="2405910000t" end="2427820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">尽力协助让爱蜜莉雅成为王</p>
<p begin="2428060000t" end="2440860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">为了达成这件事</p>
<p begin="2441100000t" end="2460600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">你的力量是不可或缺的</p>
<p begin="2476930000t" end="2488030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">说什么蠢话…</p>
<p begin="2488270000t" end="2514430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">这个提案也太过扭曲了</p>
<p begin="2518180000t" end="2533850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">难道你是打算原谅我吗</p>
<p begin="2534090000t" end="2556990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">如果要说原谅还是不原谅的话</p>
<p begin="2557230000t" end="2580460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">那我的答案是绝对不会原谅你</p>
<p begin="2585620000t" end="2608700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">但那只是我心态上的问题而已</p>
<p begin="2625260000t" end="2654500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">此时的你还并没有做出任何致命的事情</p>
<p begin="2658170000t" end="2676430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">只要我先一步解决的话</p>
<p begin="2676670000t" end="2682950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">对吧</p>
<p begin="2686780000t" end="2715840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">没有这么刚好的事情吧</p>
<p begin="2716080000t" end="2745410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我可是最喜欢这种刚好的事情了呢</p>
<p begin="2749550000t" end="2774740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">等爱蜜莉雅努力并成为王的时候</p>
<p begin="2774990000t" end="2798910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">我会在一旁祝福著她</p>
<p begin="2803120000t" end="2830530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">而你也来成为包围著她的其中一人吧</p>
<p begin="2837020000t" end="2856830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">先说好, 这可是强制的喔</p>
<p begin="2871830000t" end="2888650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">你打算不牺牲任何事物</p>
<p begin="2888890000t" end="2909990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">就达成自己的愿望吗</p>
<p begin="2910230000t" end="2923180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">在那之上</p>
<p begin="2923420000t" end="2941990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">为了达到那个未来</p>
<p begin="2942230000t" end="2968300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">还要以我也是必要之人为前提来思考</p>
<p begin="2975960000t" end="2997030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">你知道吗, 昴</p>
<p begin="3001090000t" end="3009230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">什么</p>
<p begin="3016420000t" end="3065310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">你明白那是多么充满了"强欲"的答案吗</p>
<p begin="3142410000t" end="3173350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">你的敌人已经成了最强的手牌</p>
<p begin="3176640000t" end="3195900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">还有什么不满的吗</p>
<p begin="3240110000t" end="3261660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">不管你怎么挣扎</p>
<p begin="3261900000t" end="3279610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">都不可能打破这个现状的</p>
<p begin="3284840000t" end="3301250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">无法让爱蜜莉雅大人振作起来</p>
<p begin="3301490000t" end="3315550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">没办法解除结界</p>
<p begin="3321490000t" end="3340680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">圣域会被雪覆盖</p>
<p begin="3340920000t" end="3361710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">宅邸也会沉没在血的惨剧当中</p>
<p begin="3371470000t" end="3398090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">看来挑衅你总算是有价值了呢</p>
<p begin="3416060000t" end="3428870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">原来如此</p>
<p begin="3429110000t" end="3443300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">如你所说</p>
<p begin="3446420000t" end="3462030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">为了下一任的我</p>
<p begin="3462280000t" end="3482910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">先做点什么好像也不错</p>
<p begin="3494630000t" end="3524710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">那代表你愿意接受我的提案了吧</p>
<p begin="3557130000t" end="3570860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">这样的话</p>
<p begin="3571100000t" end="3590600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">我就要开始行动了</p>
<p begin="3600440000t" end="3610310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">昴</p>
<p begin="3620230000t" end="3635630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">圣域的大雪</p>
<p begin="3635870000t" end="3649140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">还有宅邸的袭击</p>
<p begin="3649380000t" end="3659010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">都会在3天后发生</p>
<p begin="3663690000t" end="3678440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">希望你尽力而为</p>
<p begin="3678680000t" end="3694080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">然后惨败吧</p>
<p begin="3694320000t" end="3707170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">随便你说</p>
<p begin="3749720000t" end="3774090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">罗兹瓦尔, 看你疯狂成那样</p>
<p begin="3774340000t" end="3793500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">还是化上小丑的妆吧</p>
<p begin="3799970000t" end="3826720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">同样身为被命运捉弄的小丑们</p>
<p begin="3826960000t" end="3850260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">让我们堂堂正正来比一场吧</p>
<p begin="3855090000t" end="3884150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">(STRAIGHT BET 孤注一掷)</p>
<p begin="3907820000t" end="3935790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">你跟朋友耍的小聪明<br />现在状况如何</p>
<p begin="3943290000t" end="3953420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">你才是</p>
<p begin="3953670000t" end="3977910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">你可以接受罗兹瓦尔的行动吗</p>
<p begin="3978150000t" end="3987800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">对拉姆来说</p>
<p begin="3988040000t" end="4020940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">该放在首位的只有一件事而已</p>
<p begin="4027040000t" end="4055880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">那是绝对不会动摇的</p>
<p begin="4061820000t" end="4092540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">所以不要再期待<br />有什么能动摇拉姆的心了</p>
<p begin="4092780000t" end="4111260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">没有什么是绝对的</p>
<p begin="4111500000t" end="4125440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">说话小心点</p>
<p begin="4147550000t" end="4165900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你还对爱蜜莉雅大人有所期待吗</p>
<p begin="4169960000t" end="4188230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">是啊, 我既期待</p>
<p begin="4188470000t" end="4199210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">也相信著她喔</p>
<p begin="4207570000t" end="4240840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">爱蜜莉雅大人还没找到被阻碍的原因</p>
<p begin="4251780000t" end="4262830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">只要这点不解决的话</p>
<p begin="4263080000t" end="4274450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">不管试几次都是一样的</p>
<p begin="4282650000t" end="4304320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">书上所写的已经产生偏差</p>
<p begin="4309470000t" end="4327380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">罗兹瓦尔是自由的了</p>
<p begin="4357840000t" end="4377910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">竟然还会给我建议</p>
<p begin="4378150000t" end="4396590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">那家伙该不会是喜欢我吧</p>
<p begin="4396830000t" end="4417390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">你还在说这种话</p>
<p begin="4417630000t" end="4427790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">被本人听到的话</p>
<p begin="4428030000t" end="4444990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">可是会气到不行的喔</p>
<p begin="4451350000t" end="4458170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">不过现况而言</p>
<p begin="4458410000t" end="4480130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">帮助边境伯的拉姆小姐</p>
<p begin="4480380000t" end="4497210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">对我们来说是敌人对吧</p>
<p begin="4501120000t" end="4513580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">拉姆是敌人?</p>
<p begin="4549270000t" end="4589990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">我已经知道菜月先生<br />有多信赖拉姆小姐了啦</p>
<p begin="4590230000t" end="4598740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">所以说</p>
<p begin="4598980000t" end="4615700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">重点的边境伯那边呢</p>
<p begin="4618970000t" end="4633340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">目前还不错</p>
<p begin="4636780000t" end="4656970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">赌局已经成立了</p>
<p begin="4657210000t" end="4672240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">那真是太好了</p>
<p begin="4677080000t" end="4713720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">不过边境伯应该没什么输过的经验</p>
<p begin="4713960000t" end="4732380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">才会接受这个提案的吧</p>
<p begin="4739880000t" end="4758510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">然后, 接下来就是…</p>
<p begin="4770070000t" end="4790970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">加菲尔对吧</p>
<p begin="4824720000t" end="4835950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">在那之前</p>
<p begin="4836190000t" end="4853730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">我想先确认一件事可以吗</p>
<p begin="4868180000t" end="4877940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我知道了</p>
<p begin="4882470000t" end="4902590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">我会照我们所讨论的去行动</p>
<p begin="4909040000t" end="4930680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">然后, 关于爱蜜莉雅大人…</p>
<p begin="4944660000t" end="4969080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">只有这个不能假手他人</p>
<p begin="4976030000t" end="5001970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">只能靠我自己才对</p>
<p begin="5022590000t" end="5055210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我还没有触碰过爱蜜莉雅的伤痛</p>
<p begin="5061540000t" end="5086170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">结果每次都只是害怕面对而已</p>
<p begin="5089530000t" end="5105310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">就是啊</p>
<p begin="5105550000t" end="5125230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">别这么纯情好吗</p>
<p begin="5125470000t" end="5137320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">你啊</p>
<p begin="5137560000t" end="5176870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">所以你做好要去触碰她伤痛的觉悟了吗</p>
<p begin="5182580000t" end="5209720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">我是做好了要开口问她的觉悟了啦</p>
<p begin="5215730000t" end="5229330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">和面对加菲尔不同</p>
<p begin="5229580000t" end="5245150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">没有死亡的风险啦</p>
<p begin="5248970000t" end="5277690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我有点烦恼这边到底该不该笑呢</p>
<p begin="5277930000t" end="5290290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">比起那个</p>
<p begin="5290540000t" end="5315160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">你也加入到这个赢面不大的赌局了呢</p>
<p begin="5315400000t" end="5327260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">是啊</p>
<p begin="5333360000t" end="5364280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">搁下胜算高的去选择没什么赢面的一边</p>
<p begin="5372090000t" end="5385570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">这还是第一次呢</p>
<p begin="5459320000t" end="5468450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">我就想到这里的话</p>
<p begin="5468690000t" end="5484330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">一定能够见到你的</p>
<p begin="5484580000t" end="5495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">琉兹</p>
<p begin="5498950000t" end="5513970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">从你刚刚的发言</p>
<p begin="5514210000t" end="5552670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">你好像已经对老朽的事情非常清楚了呢</p>
<p begin="5562590000t" end="5574660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">如你所说</p>
<p begin="5574900000t" end="5593280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">大部分的资讯我都已经掌握了</p>
<p begin="5593520000t" end="5613060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">像是这里的目的之类的呢</p>
<p begin="5628850000t" end="5645170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">罗兹小鬼等待的人</p>
<p begin="5645420000t" end="5669660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">就是斯小鬼的意思吗…</p>
<p begin="5669900000t" end="5699120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">抱歉, 那个展开已经没机会了</p>
<p begin="5711850000t" end="5745230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">而且现在正是和罗兹瓦尔的对决当中</p>
<p begin="5749230000t" end="5774560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">我希望结果对所有人来说都是好的</p>
<p begin="5774800000t" end="5809470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">所以希望琉兹小姐也能够帮助我</p>
<p begin="5817910000t" end="5853080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">你是指用使徒的权限叫老朽帮忙吗</p>
<p begin="5859100000t" end="5878380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我不打算依靠指挥权</p>
<p begin="5889160000t" end="5914730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">所以我是来和琉兹对话的</p>
<p begin="5934180000t" end="5966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">男生总是喜欢这样耍帅呢</p>
<p begin="5969830000t" end="5992050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">所以呢, 你想知道什么</p>
<p begin="5995490000t" end="6008470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">简单来说</p>
<p begin="6008710000t" end="6045220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我想请教能够解放圣域的方法</p>
<p begin="6053730000t" end="6092470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">虽然我知道琉兹小姐<br />其实是反对解放圣域的</p>
<p begin="6102160000t" end="6131070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">老朽反对解放圣域?</p>
<p begin="6131310000t" end="6161010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">咦, 难不成你并不反对吗</p>
<p begin="6177580000t" end="6197050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">咦, 那怎么可能</p>
<p begin="6197290000t" end="6212640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">不然那个时候为什么…</p>
<p begin="6239590000t" end="6273020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">但老朽也不会说你的疑问是毫无根据</p>
<p begin="6281840000t" end="6311260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">斯小鬼对加小鬼是怎么想的</p>
<p begin="6326500000t" end="6360540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">大概没办法回避和他的冲突吧</p>
<p begin="6383740000t" end="6393430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">是吗</p>
<p begin="6393670000t" end="6402040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">但是</p>
<p begin="6407670000t" end="6440440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">在那之后是否还能重修旧好</p>
<p begin="6440680000t" end="6458160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">不试试看是不会知道的</p>
<p begin="6480900000t" end="6497700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">为了做出这个判断</p>
<p begin="6503720000t" end="6529920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">我也必须更了解他才行</p>
<p begin="6557180000t" end="6587060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">看来你很擅长哄骗老人呢</p>
<p begin="6587380000t" end="6597830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">斯小鬼</p>
<p begin="6638850000t" end="6669240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">你听魔女大人说过老朽的事了吧</p>
<p begin="6677520000t" end="6710800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">例如老朽是琉兹•梅耶尔的复制体</p>
<p begin="6711040000t" end="6744670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">或是制造复制体的目的等等…</p>
<p begin="6744910000t" end="6764350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">还有不老不死的实验</p>
<p begin="6768490000t" end="6792260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">以及琉兹你们就是成功案例等等</p>
<p begin="6803980000t" end="6829310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">现在也还是为了持续生成复制体</p>
<p begin="6829550000t" end="6856010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">而守护, 管理著魔水晶</p>
<p begin="6856260000t" end="6883000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">担负著监督者的角色</p>
<p begin="6889330000t" end="6909380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">由老朽们4个人轮流执行</p>
<p begin="6914310000t" end="6926540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">关于最初的4人的事</p>
<p begin="6926780000t" end="6938620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我已经听过了</p>
<p begin="6941900000t" end="6968280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">那么除了琉兹以外还有3个人吗</p>
<p begin="7011010000t" end="7029590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">我的名字是菜月昴</p>
<p begin="7033490000t" end="7054140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">琉兹, 你的名字是</p>
<p begin="7067030000t" end="7089290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">老朽的名字是琉兹•阿尔玛</p>
<p begin="7092340000t" end="7127110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">是最初的4个复制体当中的1个</p>
<p begin="7132650000t" end="7140450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">阿尔玛</p>
<p begin="7144030000t" end="7163870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">老朽是琉兹•毕尔玛</p>
<p begin="7170360000t" end="7190240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">第一次和我见面的琉兹</p>
<p begin="7190480000t" end="7205730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">称呼自己为毕尔玛</p>
<p begin="7211830000t" end="7243060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">虽然我一开始就没有要隐瞒的意思</p>
<p begin="7249860000t" end="7274940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不过到底为什么要做这么麻烦的事情</p>
<p begin="7281740000t" end="7315110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">老朽们复制体的身体并非血肉之躯</p>
<p begin="7315350000t" end="7348190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">而是用类似于欧德的玛那构筑而成的</p>
<p begin="7352880000t" end="7378900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">玛那会随著活动而消耗</p>
<p begin="7379140000t" end="7413000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">要一整天不断活动是不可能的</p>
<p begin="7416670000t" end="7439560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">是这样啊, 和精灵一样</p>
<p begin="7439800000t" end="7466920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">所以才用轮替的方式来完成任务吗</p>
<p begin="7473640000t" end="7480540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">但是…</p>
<p begin="7484110000t" end="7497230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">你们能接受吗</p>
<p begin="7506760000t" end="7526800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">斯小鬼是个好孩子呢</p>
<p begin="7549300000t" end="7568340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">但是, 琉兹•西玛</p>
<p begin="7572170000t" end="7596380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">最初的4人中唯一缺失的人</p>
<p begin="7596620000t" end="7617280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">只有她是例外</p>
<p begin="7624000000t" end="7639030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">琉兹•西玛</p>
<p begin="7645200000t" end="7655900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">不会说出去的</p>
<p begin="7660200000t" end="7688700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">老朽以琉兹•西玛的名字发誓</p>
<p begin="7697140000t" end="7713430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">大约十年前</p>
<p begin="7713680000t" end="7729640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">引起了问题呢</p>
<p begin="7734130000t" end="7760440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">后来就被拔除监督者的身分</p>
<p begin="7760680000t" end="7794180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">并和其他的复制体一起<br />潜伏于森林当中</p>
<p begin="7799650000t" end="7822530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">因此现在的监督者</p>
<p begin="7822770000t" end="7845580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">才会演变成只剩3人</p>
<p begin="7850500000t" end="7863530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">引起问题是指?</p>
<p begin="7870950000t" end="7902050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">她违背了和身为创造主的魔女的誓约</p>
<p begin="7902290000t" end="7916510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">进到了墓所当中</p>
<p begin="7923880000t" end="7938170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">打破了自己的誓言</p>
<p begin="7938420000t" end="7987320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">只为了带回挑战墓所试炼<br />而回不来的加小鬼</p>
<p begin="8002400000t" end="8023800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">西玛被拔除了身分之后</p>
<p begin="8024040000t" end="8041350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">老朽也从未再见过她</p>
<p begin="8048230000t" end="8063200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">但是, 加小鬼的话</p>
<p begin="8067670000t" end="8113080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">如果见过和老朽们<br />没有共通记忆的西玛也不奇怪</p>
<p begin="8117380000t" end="8138280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">琉兹你们所没有的记忆</p>
<p begin="8144530000t" end="8155050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">那就是加小鬼</p>
<p begin="8155300000t" end="8187370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">在墓所的试炼中看到的过去</p>
<p begin="8196190000t" end="8236750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">斯小鬼已经知道加小鬼家的事了吧</p>
<p begin="8251050000t" end="8282630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">法兰黛莉卡是和加菲尔同母异父的姊弟</p>
<p begin="8286770000t" end="8303660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">然后只有亚人的血较稀薄的法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="8303900000t" end="8326560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">在10年前走出了圣域</p>
<p begin="8348280000t" end="8371470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">为什么法兰黛莉卡要离开圣域呢</p>
<p begin="8388340000t" end="8419530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">我应该是想制造一个</p>
<p begin="8426800000t" end="8445930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">哪一天结界被解开以后</p>
<p begin="8450540000t" end="8490850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">让圣域的居民愿意<br />往外面世界踏出一步的契机吧</p>
<p begin="8496010000t" end="8517090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">或者是说, 容身之地吧</p>
<p begin="8528810000t" end="8545720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">她是这么说的</p>
<p begin="8554780000t" end="8562060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">该不会</p>
<p begin="8562300000t" end="8578470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">加菲尔看到的过去</p>
<p begin="8578710000t" end="8594130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">就是法兰黛莉卡离开时的事</p>
<p begin="8597420000t" end="8625770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">不, 那孩子看到的应该是…</p>
<p begin="8631230000t" end="8668790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">将加小鬼和法2个人给留下</p>
<p begin="8669040000t" end="8694250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">母亲独自离开时的场景吧</p>
<p begin="8709170000t" end="8731590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">愚蠢又可怜的加菲尔</p>
<p begin="8731830000t" end="8751290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">害怕著外面的世界</p>
<p begin="8770120000t" end="8794220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">那家伙排斥解放圣域是因为</p>
<p begin="8800000000t" end="8826080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">对选择了外面而将自己给舍弃掉的母亲</p>
<p begin="8829440000t" end="8850110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">的负面情感吗</p>
<p begin="8869720000t" end="8909360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">那孩子称呼自己为"加菲尔•汀泽尔"</p>
<p begin="8913660000t" end="8936750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">也就是母亲的姓氏</p>
<p begin="8936990000t" end="8981710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">老朽想应该是要让自己无法忘记<br />才这样称呼的吧</p>
<p begin="8991320000t" end="9029070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">但那是因为愤怒还是悲伤</p>
<p begin="9033130000t" end="9046730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">知道的恐怕就只有</p>
<p begin="9046970000t" end="9081680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">那孩子和西玛而已了</p>
<p begin="9140750000t" end="9150550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="9195300000t" end="9205320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">昴</p>
<p begin="9212200000t" end="9227930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">怎么了吗爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
