<p begin="9554670000t" end="9564270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">谢谢</p>
<p begin="9611300000t" end="9620180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="9620420000t" end="9642270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">你愿意和我说说</p>
<p begin="9642510000t" end="9662950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">在试炼当中见到了什么吗</p>
<p begin="9680140000t" end="9697950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">"说出来就会变轻松"</p>
