<p begin="9722380000t" end="9737860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">不过如果你愿意说出来的话</p>
<p begin="9738100000t" end="9748840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">至少我能和你一起烦恼</p>
<p begin="9755400000t" end="9774260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">虽然不知道我靠不靠得住</p>
<p begin="9778870000t" end="9808160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">不过你愿意给我这个<br />和你一起战斗的资格吗</p>
<p begin="9866820000t" end="9876800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">昴</p>
<p begin="9881020000t" end="9912650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">昴你相信我</p>
<p begin="10000020000t" end="10010010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">我…</p>
<p begin="10017820000t" end="10038440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">我看见的过去…</p>
<p begin="10044770000t" end="10081280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">大概是我在沉睡前的记忆</p>
<p begin="10090660000t" end="10116240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">我从来没和昴说过</p>
<p begin="10121240000t" end="10146260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">我曾经一直待在冰柱中的事对吧</p>
<p begin="10150180000t" end="10167730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">冰柱中?</p>
<p begin="10172220000t" end="10205060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">我一直被困在森林里的冰柱之中</p>
<p begin="10212400000t" end="10242620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">在帕克找到我之前</p>
<p begin="10248230000t" end="10263230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">很长一段时间</p>
<p begin="10269290000t" end="10295170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">我一直都在冰柱中沉睡著</p>
<p begin="10306650000t" end="10315980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">那是什么时候的事</p>
<p begin="10316220000t" end="10348720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">应该是从6还7岁开始</p>
<p begin="10348960000t" end="10363060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">一直到森林被冰封起来为止</p>
<p begin="10363290000t" end="10379820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">都和大家生活在一起的</p>
<p begin="10380060000t" end="10387480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">应该?</p>
<p begin="10387710000t" end="10421730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">因为在那之前的事情我想不太起来了</p>
<p begin="10427280000t" end="10442530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">爱蜜莉雅的家人呢</p>
<p begin="10448860000t" end="10477230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">森林里并没有我的家人</p>
<p begin="10484760000t" end="10511550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">不过有一个像是我母亲一般的人</p>
<p begin="10526160000t" end="10533330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">咦</p>
<p begin="10547390000t" end="10555610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">为什么</p>
<p begin="10569750000t" end="10586250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">妈妈?</p>
<p begin="10622330000t" end="10633820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">冷静一点</p>
<p begin="10634060000t" end="10645920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">慢慢来就好</p>
<p begin="10660850000t" end="10683460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">大家…怎么样了</p>
<p begin="10692680000t" end="10732690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">和我一样被困在冰雪之中</p>
<p begin="10740900000t" end="10758580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">我在森林里生活</p>
<p begin="10758820000t" end="10790440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">一直等待著大家苏醒</p>
<p begin="10794190000t" end="10810140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">但是和帕克一起等了好久</p>
<p begin="10817250000t" end="10837490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">那一天却始终没有到来</p>
<p begin="10847020000t" end="10871360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">所以我离开了森林</p>
<p begin="10879880000t" end="10894300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">参加了王选</p>
<p begin="10907350000t" end="10933790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">为什么森林的事情会和王选牵扯在一起</p>
<p begin="10940590000t" end="10968120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">因为罗兹瓦尔和我约定好了</p>
