<p begin="11122150000t" end="11147020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">抱持著觉悟来参加王选的</p>
<p begin="11151400000t" end="11183370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">但我却是因为这么这么私人的理由</p>
<p begin="11190950000t" end="11205320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">那就是你说的</p>
