<p begin="11318420000t" end="11339980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">并不会影响做这件事的伟大程度</p>
<p begin="11369120000t" end="11391590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">真的很谢谢你</p>
<p begin="11433540000t" end="11442070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">爱蜜莉雅</p>
