<p begin="11771540000t" end="11794520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">抱歉, 爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="11825530000t" end="11834890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">好痛</p>
